divs: sighting detailsi have recorded footage on various days of what i believe is a ufo, in my videos most of the footage has been taken from my bedroom accept for the last footage which was taken from my back garden using a tripod. also during the period of 19th-24th may 2007 i have experienced seeing flashing lights which have come out of this object in the sky, this was before i just went into my local pub with my mates on the 19th may and have also witnessed as a passenger in car some sort ufo triangle craft elevating in the sky above the 3 objects which were in a triangle formation this was when my mate was driving down the m6 on the motorway on the 24th may. i have compiled all my recordings into one video. this is not the complete recording, it has been shortened to 10 minutes. please click on the link below to see: http:\\video.google.co.uk\videoplay?docid=2138839065324379175 i have also seen the objects in this video above the past 2 nights, in different positions and we are now in july. would be very interested for feedback please. looking forward to hearing from you soon yours faithfully roberto pall
